						<summary>

						<p>On a slab in front of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> of the Mādhavasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated <hi rend="italic">Kīlaka, Āśvija,</hi> śu. 15; Written in late characters.</p>						

						<p>Records the receipt of the principal with interest issued by Nedhaṁ (Nadala?)-Yallappa to Basuvaya and other <hi rend="italic">Kāpus</hi> (Cf. No. 36 (A.R. 45 of 1953-54). Refers to the Chenna-kēśava temple.</p>						

